Package: SAoTD
Type: Package
Title: Sentiment Analysis of Twitter Data
Version: 1.0
Date: 2018-01-17
Author: Evan L. Munson
Maintainer: Evan L. Munson <evan.l.munson@email.com>
Description: This analytic is an in initial forray into sentiment analysis.  This analytic will allow a user to access the Twitter API (once they create their own developer account), ingest tweets of their interest, clean / tidy data, perform topic modeling if interested, compute sentiment scores utilizing the Bing Lexicon, and output visualizations.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.12.14), plyr, dplyr, stringr, tidytext, twitteR, purrr, tidyr, igraph, ggraph, widyr, ggplot2, scales, reshape2, topicmodels, ldatuning, lubridate, utils, shiny, stats, magrittr, httr, base64enc
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
